  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large bamboo steamer over medium heat.",
    "add the cumin seeds, coriander seeds, and fenugreek seeds, and let them sizzle for 1 minute.",
    "add the garam masala, red chili powder, and ground cumin, and stir for 1 minute.",
    "add the chicken thighs and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the yogurt, dark soft brown sugar, and salt, and stir well.",
    "close the bamboo steamer and steam the chicken for 20 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "fluff the chicken with a fork and stir in the fresh cilantro.",
    "serve hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
